    "Html": "Hi All,<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCould anyone please fill me in on the process of accessing resources (in this case an image) from downloaded XAPs using Prism.  In particular, how should the resources be included in the project, where do they go when the XAP is downloaded and then how should they be referenced?<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThe following is a snippet from the app to display a png file.  The image is visible in the XAML preview, but it isn't displayed in the application because it can't locate the png. (I'm 99% sure)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">\r\n<p>&lt;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">StackPanel</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> x</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">:</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\">Name</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;ValidUploadIcon&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Width</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;30&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> HorizontalAlignment</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Center&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> VerticalAlignment</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Center&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Visibility</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Visible&quot;&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Image</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\">Source</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;Img/tick.png&quot;</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#ff0000\"> Height</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">=&quot;15&quot;&gt;&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">Image</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#a31515\">StackPanel</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">&gt;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCheers,<br>\r\nJeff\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></p>\r\n",
